      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-ric      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/No stampa                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-stp      .
       pre-tip-fun-999.
