      *                  * Operazioni relative all'operazione di paga- *
      *                  * mento                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
       det-srd-scf-425.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se la scadenza non porta un numero pa-  *
      *                      * gamento si escludono tutti i controlli  *
      *                      * sulle operazioni relative al pagamento  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sfs-num-pgf       =    zero
                     go to det-srd-scf-625.
       det-srd-scf-450.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura record [sfp]                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NUMSFP    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      rf-sfs-num-pgf       to   rf-sfp-num-pgf         .
           move      "pgm/scf/fls/ioc/obj/iofsfp"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-sfp                 .
       det-srd-scf-475.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se operazione di pagamento non esisten- *
      *                      * te in archivio distinte si escludono    *
      *                      * tutti i controlli sulle operazioni re-  *
      *                      * lative al pagamento                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-srd-scf-625.
       det-srd-scf-500.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se la data di registrazione pagamento   *
      *                      * e' superiore alla data di riferimento   *
      *                      * per la determinazione si escludono tut- *
      *                      * ti i controlli sulle operazioni relati- *
      *                      * ve al pagamento                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sfp-dtr-pgf       >    w-det-srd-scf-drd
                     go to det-srd-scf-625.
       det-srd-scf-525.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Pagamento                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "PAG"                to   w-det-srd-scf-suo      .
       det-srd-scf-625.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Fine controlli su operazioni relative   *
      *                      * al pagamento                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     det-srd-scf-800.
       det-srd-scf-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione dello status della scadenza in   *
      *              * funzione della sigla dell'ultima operazione e-  *
      *              * seguita sulla scadenza                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-srd-scf-suo    =    "REG"
                     move  "A"            to   w-det-srd-scf-sts
           else if   w-det-srd-scf-suo    =    "SSC" or
                     w-det-srd-scf-suo    =    "PAG"
                     move  "C"            to   w-det-srd-scf-sts
           else      move  spaces         to   w-det-srd-scf-sts      .
       det-srd-scf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione numero protocollo iva                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-prt-iva-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione valore in uscita editato        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se valori in input ammissibili             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-prt-iva-fnt    =    zero or
                     w-det-prt-iva-ddo    =    zero or
                     w-det-prt-iva-ndo    =    spaces
                     go to det-prt-iva-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore records [mgr] trovati *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-prt-iva-ctr      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work per identificazione regi-  *
      *              * strazione contabile                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-prt-iva-wdr      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-prt-iva-wnp      .
       det-prt-iva-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su file [mgr] per chiave 'TARDOC'         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "TARDOC    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      "F"                  to   rf-mgr-tip-arc         .
           move      w-det-prt-iva-ddo    to   rf-mgr-dat-doc         .
           move      w-det-prt-iva-ndo    to   rf-mgr-num-doc         .
           move      w-det-prt-iva-fnt    to   rf-mgr-cod-arc         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-dat-reg         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-num-prt         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-mgr-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su esito operazione                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-prt-iva-500.
       det-prt-iva-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale record [mgr]                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgr                 .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se 'At End'                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-prt-iva-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgr-tip-arc       not  = "F"               or
                     rf-mgr-dat-doc       not  = w-det-prt-iva-ddo or
                     rf-mgr-num-doc       not  = w-det-prt-iva-ndo or
                     rf-mgr-cod-arc       not  = w-det-prt-iva-fnt
                     go to det-prt-iva-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore records [mgr] trovati      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-det-prt-iva-ctr      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento work per identificazione regi-    *
      *              * strazione contabile                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-prt-iva-wdr    =    zero and
                     w-det-prt-iva-wnp    =    zero
                     move  rf-mgr-dat-reg to   w-det-prt-iva-wdr
                     move  rf-mgr-num-prt to   w-det-prt-iva-wnp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo su lettura sequenziale record [mgr]     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-prt-iva-200.
       det-prt-iva-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su numero record incontrati                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-prt-iva-ctr    =    zero or
                     w-det-prt-iva-ctr    >    1
                     go to det-prt-iva-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura record [mgt]                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NL"                 to   f-cfr                  .
           move      "DATREG    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-det-prt-iva-wdr    to   rf-mgt-dat-reg         .
           move      w-det-prt-iva-wnp    to   rf-mgt-num-prt         .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgt"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-mgt                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se lettura errata : uscita                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-prt-iva-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione stringa per protocollo iva         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da effettuare                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgt-cod-num       =    zero and
                     rf-mgt-prt-iva       =    zero
                     go to det-prt-iva-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero giornale iva                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se necessario                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mgt-cod-num       =    zero
                     go to det-prt-iva-520.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * String                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           string    rf-mgt-cod-num
                               delimited  by   size
                     "-"       delimited  by   size
                                          into w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
       det-prt-iva-520.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero protocollo iva                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Editing                                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   p-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   p-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   p-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   p-edm                  .
           move      rf-mgt-prt-iva       to   p-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * String                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           string    p-edt
                               delimited  by   spaces
                                          into w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
       det-prt-iva-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Allineamento a destra                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-prt-iva-pie    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           move      10                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           perform   all-str-adx-000      thru all-str-adx-999        .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
       det-prt-iva-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su valore di uscita                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-det-prt-iva-pie    not  = spaces
                     go to det-prt-iva-900.
           move      "Indeterm. "         to   w-det-prt-iva-pie      .
       det-prt-iva-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-prt-iva-999.
       det-prt-iva-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per allineamenti a destra o a sinistra oppure *
      *    * al centro di campi alfanumerici di varia lunghezza, fi-   *
      *    * no ad un massimo di 240 caratteri, oppure per il conca-   *
      *    * tenamento, con o senza separazione, di max 10 substrin-   *
      *    * ghe in una unica substringa                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/std/prg/cpy/wallstr0.cps"                   .

